item.description: sourceware.org Name Description ar Create, modify, and extract from archives nm List symbols from object files objcopy Copy and translate object files objdump Display information from object files ranlib Generate index to archive contents size List section sizes and total size strings List printable strings from files strip Discard symbols c++filt Filter to demangle encoded C++ symbols cxxfilt MS-DOS name for c++filt addr2line Convert addresses to file and line windmc Generator for Windows message resources windres Manipulate Windows resources dlltool Create files needed to build and use DLLs readelf Display the contents of ELF format files elfedit Update ELF header and property of ELF files
